                        <interp inst="t18450203-name-349" type="given" value="CHARLES FREDERICK"></interp>CHARLES FREDERICK BLACKIE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am apprentice on board the <hi rend="italic">Seringa<lb></lb>patam.</hi> I lost some of these articles—they were safe on the 10th of Jan., a little before five o'clock, when I went to tea, and when I came back they were gone—these jackets, and some other things, are mine—the <hi rend="italic">Seringa-patam</hi> was then in the dock.</p>
